          "order": 2,
          "title": "BROTHERHOOD AND BETRAYAL",
          "summary": "Sam Bankman-Fried and Gary Wang had been friends since their teens. They met during a five-week summer program for mathematically talented high school students in 2008. Bankman-Fried and Wang worked together for nearly all of their adult lives. This article looks at Gary Wang, his past, and his role with FTX. Wang was mostly in the background, creating the platforms and engines that the company used.",
